snippet.title: Shin Megami Tensei III Nocturne HD Remaster — Factions & Choices Trailer | PS4, Nintendo Switch, PC
snippet.description:
The shape of the new world is in your hands – but whose Reason will you align with? Shin Megami Tensei III Nocturne HD Remaster releases May 25th. 

Pre-order now: atlus.com/smt3/
